<metal:use-macro use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master">
  <metal:content fill-slot="content-core">

    <h1 tal:content="view/title">样本明细（占位页）</h1>

    <p class="discreet">
      这是新建的明细页面。现在不接收任何参数；后面再加筛选即可。
    </p>

    <table class="listing table table-bordered table-responsive"
           style="width:100%; table-layout:fixed;">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width:25%;">样品编号</th>
          <th style="width:20%;">中心编码</th>
          <th style="width:20%;">状态</th>
          <th>备注</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tal:rows repeat="row view/demo_rows">
          <tr>
            <td tal:content="row/sample_id">AR0001</td>
            <td tal:content="row/center_code">01</td>
            <td tal:content="row/status">received</td>
            <td>（演示数据）</td>
          </tr>
        </tal:rows>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <a tal:attributes="href context/absolute_url">返回当前位置</a>
    </p>

  </metal:content>
</metal:use-macro>
